{"thag10.7:0.1":"Theragatha 10.7 ","thag10.7:0.2":"Dasakanipata ","thag10.7:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag10.7:0.4":"(Apara) Gotamattheragatha ","thag10.7:1.1":"“Vijaneyya sakam attham, ","thag10.7:1.2":"Avalokeyyatha pavacanam; ","thag10.7:1.3":"Yancettha assa patirupam, ","thag10.7:1.4":"Samannam ajjhupagatassa. ","thag10.7:2.1":"Mittam idha ca kalyanam, ","thag10.7:2.2":"Sikkha vipulam samadanam; ","thag10.7:2.3":"Sussusa ca garunam, ","thag10.7:2.4":"Etam samanassa patirupam. ","thag10.7:3.1":"Buddhesu sagaravata, ","thag10.7:3.2":"Dhamme apaciti yathabhutam; ","thag10.7:3.3":"Sanghe ca cittikaro, ","thag10.7:3.4":"Etam samanassa patirupam. ","thag10.7:4.1":"Acaragocare yutto, ","thag10.7:4.2":"Ajivo sodhito agarayho; ","thag10.7:4.3":"Cittassa ca santhapanam, ","thag10.7:4.4":"Etam samanassa patirupam. ","thag10.7:5.1":"Carittam atha varittam, ","thag10.7:5.2":"Iriyapathiyam pasadaniyam; ","thag10.7:5.3":"Adhicitte ca ayogo, ","thag10.7:5.4":"Etam samanassa patirupam. ","thag10.7:6.1":"Arannakani senasanani, ","thag10.7:6.2":"Pantani appasaddani; ","thag10.7:6.3":"Bhajitabbani munina, ","thag10.7:6.4":"Etam samanassa patirupam. ","thag10.7:7.1":"Silanca bahusaccanca, ","thag10.7:7.2":"Dhammanam pavicayo yathabhutam; ","thag10.7:7.3":"Saccanam abhisamayo, ","thag10.7:7.4":"Etam samanassa patirupam. ","thag10.7:8.1":"Bhaveyya ca aniccanti, ","thag10.7:8.2":"Anattasannam asubhasannanca; ","thag10.7:8.3":"Lokamhi ca anabhiratim, ","thag10.7:8.4":"Etam samanassa patirupam. ","thag10.7:9.1":"Bhaveyya ca bojjhange, ","thag10.7:9.2":"Iddhipadani indriyani balani; ","thag10.7:9.3":"Atthangamaggamariyam, ","thag10.7:9.4":"Etam samanassa patirupam. ","thag10.7:10.1":"Tanham pajaheyya muni, ","thag10.7:10.2":"Samulake asave padaleyya; ","thag10.7:10.3":"Vihareyya vippamutto, ","thag10.7:10.4":"Etam samanassa patirupan”ti. ","thag10.7:10.5":"… Gotamo thero … ","thag10.7:10.6":"Dasakanipato nitthito. ","thag10.7:11.0":"Tatruddanam ","thag10.7:11.1":"Kaludayi ca so thero, ","thag10.7:11.2":"ekavihari ca kappino; ","thag10.7:11.3":"Culapanthako kappo ca, ","thag10.7:11.4":"upaseno ca gotamo; ","thag10.7:11.5":"Sattime dasake thera, ","thag10.7:11.6":"gathayo cettha sattatiti. "}